#Control statement
SELECTION STATEMENT: CHOICES ARE MADE AS PER CONDITION
-> if construct
-> if-else
-> if-else-if
-> nested if-else-if
-> switch-case

ITERATIVE STATEMENT: REPEATS A CONDITION
-> while loop
-> do-while loop
-> for loop

UNCONDITIONAL CONTROL STATEMENT: IT TRANSFERS CONTROL-FLOW TO SOME OTHER SECTION OF THE PROGRAM WITHOUT THE NEED OF A CONDITION.
-> break
-> continue
-> goto statement